org.diirt.graphene.profile.impl

Class ProfileParallelHistogram1D

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.diirt.graphene.profile.Profiler
      • org.diirt.graphene.profile.ProfileGraph2D<AreaGraph2DRenderer,Cell1DDataset>
        • org.diirt.graphene.profile.impl.ProfileHistogram1D
          • org.diirt.graphene.profile.impl.ProfileParallelHistogram1D

  • public class ProfileParallelHistogram1D
extends ProfileHistogram1D
    Handles profiling for Histogram1D in parallel (by threading). Takes a Histogram1D dataset and repeatedly renders with several threads of AreaGraph2DRenderer objects.
    Author:
    carcassi, asbarber
